content.p: Impact Acceleration Account Project Officer, Financial & Business Services Kate is the Impact Accelartion Account Project Officer, supporting projects and programmes, for institutional Knowledge Exchange grants awarded to the University. These are predominantly based around the Higher Education Innovation Fund and Impact Acceleration Account. These grants are intended to support, accelerate, and help to realize the impact and benefits of the University's research and training outside of academia. https://www.nottingham.ac.uk/fabs/research-innovation/ipcommercialisation/knowledge-exchange-funding.aspx Get in touch: research.innovation@nottingham.ac.uk Jubilee Conference Centre Jubilee Campus Triumph Road Nottingham, NG8 1DH
